{"tid":1533491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［冷氣軍師］要成功就要有新策略","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:17:19.000Z","uid":99125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4e0e6e6d0d242cd9366fb77796d6f5a9603dd5","tid":1533491,"uid":99125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"係無呀，等死啦香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5942eeb6659594db6c99fd372e2798271c6d8e9c","tid":1533491,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=e425debe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"22f95ab49b73034b18c28aa20e1c536a73d39c6e","tid":1533491,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"入黎了解真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［整合］聽日早上7點 光復大埔何郭佩珍中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbe33a0234f5a59ddfd672d365f09abef201e0d4","tid":1533491,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"低風險，高回報=魔法"},{"pid":"dc26d786d599fc5438229fbfeafadd353d72691d","tid":1533491,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"同中共打持久戰無著數<br />\n一係黎一鋪大野, 逼佢出老解算數<br />\n612都係決定3點鐘, 衝政總先打開到局面<br />\n其實我地唔適合持久戰"},{"pid":"bbbe65be38a519a5d334d04b80e6e90191ada6f1","tid":1533491,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM80cCFS.png&h=5da9f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n<strong>請瘋狂tweet and retweet</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D54td2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D54td2.png&h=af5cfe54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVKdmy5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVKdmy5.png&h=81d6d0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Pbjg7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Pbjg7r.png&h=72df